Hey Gang 💋 
🏄🏻‍♀️Come ride my WEIV❗️❗️
Excited to announce I’m officially now on @theweivofficial 
where I will be posting all of my premium content.

📺In this 1st exclusive WEIV release, it’s the return of the fan favorite series-  Valentine Vision. I’ma take y’all ALL THE WAY behind the scenes during the making of Wild N Out Season 16. 🎬Catch me and your favorite cast members like @dcyoungfly as we return to set together after ALMOST being canceled.  

🔗 in b¡o to Subscribe to my WEIV and watch the full VLOG streaming now 🍿👀💋
